      "comment": "GRANDIOSE GIRL (6) flew the lids with a fast early split and led until late but gathered in when a neck second at this track over 352m in 19.58. Has a strong record out of this box with four wins and a minor placing from seven starts. Winning claims. TAKE OVER HAZE (5) was popular in betting last start but disappointed when 5.5 lengths away in fifth (19.85). Was in the money the start prior. Has a very good strike-rate from this draw, with four wins from nine starts. A big run wouldn't surprise. FLYING JILLIBY (4) was on speed throughout but copped a check to finish fifth (20.00) at this track over 352m in a Free For All. Rates a leading chance. OUTLAW TORQUE (2) has been freshened and can sneak into the frame on his best form.",
